channel.title: Old School Server Allstar Edited! ~Anti Null/Syi,Duping, High Alch fixed~
channel.description:
This is A classic based server. Skate-Scape! We are based off of Mod Allstars Source. Just been online for a few days and looking for players that enjoy the old 317's like these. I always Enjoyed Allstar's source. I think it just needed to be cleaned up and debugged. The server wishes all true classic lovers to join. This is a true classic not the ones that claim to be that aren't
[center]Features
Anti Nuller/Syi Real Godsword stances Customs Cheat Clients fixed Small Respectable staff team Better economy than classic Allstar All skills go to level 130[/center]
Forums: SkateScape.forumtk.net Host: Tre-Flip.no-ip.biz
Home! [IMG]http://i49.tinypic.com/2vmj249.jpg[/img]
Train With Added Npc's [IMG]http://i47.tinypic.com/11cdpb8.jpg[/img]
Same Shops Made by Mod Allstar [IMG]http://i48.tinypic.com/1428xzd.jpg[/img]
New Pkbox At Tree Gnome Hangar [IMG]http://i50.tinypic.com/2r6p4b6.jpg[/img]
